olas  , influenced by the short form   Nick ."]},{"name":"Nicolas","meanings":["From Late Greek.  See  <b>Nicholas</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Nicholas Dromsfield was born about 1176, in Whitley, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. She married Nicholas Dromsfield about 1197, in Whitley, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"about 1176–":"umbes 1176–Surnud","1172–Male":"1172–Surnud","1198–Male":"1198–Surnud","1176–Female":"1176–Surnud","1198":"1198","1176":"1176","about 1176":"umbes 1176","1172":"1172","about 1197":"umbes 1197","Whitley, Yorkshire, England":"Whitley, Yorkshire, England","of Whitley, Yorkshire, England":"Whitley, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1176–":"noin 1176–Kuollut","1172–Male":"1172–Kuollut","1198–Male":"1198–Kuollut","1176–Female":"1176–Kuollut","1198":"1198","1176":"1176","about 1176":"noin 1176","1172":"1172","about 1197":"noin 1197","Whitley, Yorkshire, England":"Whitley, Yorkshire, England","of Whitley, Yorkshire, England":"Whitley, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1176–":"environ 1176–Décédée","1172–Male":"1172–Décédé","1198–Male":"1198–Décédé","1176–Female":"1176–Décédée","1198":"1198","1176":"1176","about 1176":"environ 1176","1172":"1172","about 1197":"environ 1197","Whitley, Yorkshire, England":"Whitley, Everwyck, Angleterre","of Whitley, Yorkshire, England":"Whitley, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs Nicholas Dromsfield est née environ 1176, à Whitley, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Nicholas Dromsfield environ 1197, à Whitley, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"about 1176–":"um 1176–Verstorben","1172–Male":"1172–Verstorben","1198–Male":"1198–Verstorben","1176–Female":"1176–Verstorben","1198":"1198","1176":"1176","about 1176":"um 1176","1172":"1172","about 1197":"um 1197","Whitley, Yorkshire, England":"Whitley, Yorkshire, England","of Whitley, Yorkshire, England":"